/*

# add folders that shouldn't be ignored
!src/


!.gitignore
!README.md
!requirements.txt
!requirements-dev.txt
!pytest.ini
!results
!data
!figures
!DECISIONS.md
!FINDINGS.md

# Windows "Mark of the Web" sidecar files created when downloaded files
# are copied into WSL (NTFS Zone.Identifier alternate data streams)
*:Zone.Identifier

# compiled bytecode caches; !src/ above re-includes everything under src/
# recursively, so these need an explicit re-exclusion
__pycache__/
*.pyc